<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.10">
<l>vaitta nāḷvarai yellai kuṟukicceṉ</l>
<l>ṟeytti ḷaippataṉ muṉṉa maṭaimiṉō</l>
<l>paitta pāmpṇai yāṉṟiru vēṅkaṭa</l>
<l>moytta cōlaimoy pūntaṭan tāḻvarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before being completely exhausted by going, nearing the border</l>
<l>of the mountain on the set day approach, please,</l>
<l>those who sink into the flower tank swarmed by swarmed groves</l>
<l>of sacred Vēṅkaṭam of the one of a hooded serpent bed.</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
